  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Ferocious pygmies from the dense jungles, Flayers attack in hordes and overwhelm the unprepared. Quick and vicious, they embody the chaos of the Kurast Wilds.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Normal:</strong> Small charms, daggers</li>
    <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Magic throwing knives, runes (Tal–Ral)</li>
    <li><strong>Hell:</strong> Unique javelins, runes (Um–Mal)</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Affixes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Frenzied – Moves faster with each attack</li>
    <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Carnage – Extra damage in groups</li>
  </ul>
</section>

